      "sc:author": "Zuguang Gu",
      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.1186/s12864-018-4625-x"
      },
      "sc:description": "Enriched heatmap is a special type of heatmap which visualizes the enrichment of genomic signals on specific target regions. Here we implement enriched heatmap by ComplexHeatmap package. Since this type of heatmap is just a normal heatmap but with some special settings, with the functionality of ComplexHeatmap, it would be much easier to customize the heatmap as well as concatenating to a list of heatmaps to show correspondance between different data sources.",
